---
import smallCharacter from '../assets/about/persona.png';
---

<style>
.casestudy-contentpadding{
    padding:3vh;
}
h1{
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #5B483E;
    font-family: 'Inter Var';
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-block-start: 0px;
    margin-block-end: 0px;
}
h2{
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    color: #5B483E;
    font-family: 'Inter Var';
    font-weight: 700; /*originaly 580 */
    margin-block-start: 0px;
    margin-block-end: 0px;
}

h3{
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-family: 'Inter Var';
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 580;
    color: #515155;
    margin-block-start: 0px;
    margin-block-end: 0px;
}

h4{
    font-family: 'Inter Var';
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 580;
    color: #515155;
    margin-block-start: 0px;
    margin-block-end: 0px;
}

p {
    font-family: 'Inter Var';
    color: #515155;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3125rem;
    margin-block-start: 0px;
    margin-block-end: 0px;
}


.twoColumn{
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2, auto);
    gap: 1.5rem;
}

#flex24px{ /*24px flex */
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
}

.casestudy-container{ /*36px margin top */
margin-top: 2.25rem;
}

.casestudy-container48{
    margin-top: 3rem;
}


/**************************

        Media Query

***************************/

@media screen and (max-width:430px){ /*Sets mobile margin to 16px */

.casestudy-contentpadding{
    padding:1vh;
}
}


@media screen and (max-width: 500px){
    .threeColumn{
        grid-template-columns: none;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr;
    }
    .twoColumn{
        grid-template-columns: none;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr;
    }
    .halfWidthText{
        max-width: 100%;
    }
}

@media screen and (min-width:877px) and (max-width:1039px){
    .threeColumn{
        grid-template-columns: none;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr;
    }
    .twoColumn{
        grid-template-columns: none;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr;
    }
}

</style>

<div class="casestudy-contentpadding">
    <div id="flex24px">
        <h3>Thanks for swinging by!</h3>
        <div class="twoColumn">
            <p>I'm a recent graduate from UC Berkeley, designing in the San Francisco Bay Area.
            <br /><br />
            Although growing up, I never looked into design as a possible career, I always caught myself DIY-ing the things around me to fit the mood I was feeling at the time — from Wii remote skins to spray painting my first ever longboard.
            <br /><br />
            UX Design is where I’ve found my home in Design and Product, but I'm always curious of how far I can stretch my wings when it comes to building solutions for my community.
            </p>
            <img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src={smallCharacter.src} width={smallCharacter.width} height={smallCharacter.height} />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="casestudy-container48">
        <h4>Some things I've worked on</h4>
    </div>
</div>
